name: Kitty Dash - Brave Rocket Frontier
description:
” Highly addictive fast paced Gameplay.”
” Adorable graphic style.”
” Exciting Levels.”
___________________________________

Kitty Dash is a crazy fast action packed game that will keep you entertained for hours. The playful kitty wants to gain the maximum points, jumping from level to level.

Tap frequently above the kitty to make him jump! With higher jumps and proper precision, kitty can grab onto the maximum coins. The more jumps you will make, the more the distance you will travel and the higher score you earn!

+++ GAME FEATURES +++
Catchy music during game play
Great graphics
Easy to learn game play
Funny characters
